---

<section class="intro section-padding" id="intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro__grid">
      <div class="intro__left">
        <span class="intro__label">Optimización de Riego y Fertilización</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Maximiza el Rendimiento de tu Finca</h2>
        <p class="intro__text">
          Nuestros sensores de suelo (NPK, Humedad, pH) generan evidencia
          digital que justifica legalmente cada aporte de agua y abono en tu
          Cuaderno de Campo. Reduce costes de insumos, evita sanciones por
          incumplimiento normativo y toma decisiones basadas en datos reales.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro__right">
        <div class="intro__card glass">
          <h3 class="intro__subtitle">Evidencia Digital para SIEX</h3>
          <p class="intro__subtext">
            Cada riego, cada abonado y cada tratamiento queda registrado
            automáticamente en tu cuaderno digital con los datos de tus
            sensores como respaldo documental.
          </p>
          <div class="intro__list">
            <div class="intro__list-item">
              <span class="intro__list-icon">✓</span>
              <span>Registro automático de riegos y aportes</span>
            </div>
            <div class="intro__list-item">
              <span class="intro__list-icon">✓</span>
              <span>Validación de dosis de abono según normativa</span>
            </div>
            <div class="intro__list-item">
              <span class="intro__list-icon">✓</span>
              <span>Justificación legal de cada aporte hídrico</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    background: var(--color-white);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .intro__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro__label {
    display: block;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .intro__text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .intro__card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
    box-shadow:
      0 24px 60px rgba(11, 26, 20, 0.16),
      0 10px 24px rgba(11, 139, 245, 0.10);
    transform-origin: center bottom;
    animation: introCardReveal 1s cubic-bezier(0.18, 0.9, 0.24, 1) both;
  }

  .intro__card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -35%;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(11, 139, 245, 0.18), transparent 38%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 72%, rgba(14, 198, 170, 0.18), transparent 34%);
    opacity: 0.9;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: introCardAura 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .intro__card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    left: -35%;
    width: 30%;
    height: 150%;
    background: linear-gradient(115deg, transparent 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18) 45%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72) 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18) 55%, transparent 100%);
    transform: rotate(14deg);
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: introCardSheen 4.8s ease-in-out infinite 0.85s;
  }

  .intro__subtitle {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .intro__subtext {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .intro__list {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .intro__list-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(11, 26, 20, 0.08);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(18px);
    animation: introListItemIn 0.75s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .intro__list-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(14, 198, 170, 0.14);
    color: var(--color-turquoise);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(14, 198, 170, 0.28);
    animation: introIconPulse 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .intro__list-item:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 0.28s;
  }

  .intro__list-item:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.42s;
  }

  .intro__list-item:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 0.56s;
  }

  @keyframes introCardReveal {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: perspective(1200px) rotateX(12deg) translateY(44px) scale(0.95);
      filter: blur(12px);
    }
    60% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: perspective(1200px) rotateX(-2deg) translateY(-6px) scale(1.01);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: perspective(1200px) rotateX(0deg) translateY(0) scale(1);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes introCardSheen {
    0% {
      left: -35%;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    10% {
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    42% {
      left: 118%;
      opacity: 0.75;
    }
    100% {
      left: 118%;
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }

  @keyframes introCardAura {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: scale(1) translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.08) translate3d(1.5%, -1.5%, 0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes introListItemIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(18px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes introIconPulse {
    0%, 100% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(14, 198, 170, 0.12);
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(14, 198, 170, 0);
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .intro__card,
    .intro__card::before,
    .intro__card::after,
    .intro__list-item,
    .intro__list-icon {
      animation: none !important;
      transform: none !important;
      opacity: 1 !important;
      filter: none !important;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .intro__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 50px;
    }
    .intro__card {
      padding: 32px;
    }
  }
</style>
